	<Title>
		Is your lifestyle causing heartburn?
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Heartburn can make your chest feel like it&apos;s on fire. Consider these lifestyle changes to prevent heartburn: 1. Lose excess weight. 2. Eat smaller meals. 3. Don&apos;t wear tightfitting clothes. 4. Avoid heartburn triggers, such as alcohol, fatty foods, chocolate and mint. 5. Don&apos;t lie down soon after a meal. 6. Raise the head of your bed. 7. Stop smoking.&lt;/p&gt;
